  "body": "### Description\n\nIn the q3 dev-ui the log panel is diffcult for me to grab and enlarge / shrink.\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/assets/1223135/6c58fb6d-a756-4413-97c5-6212b8df6313)\r\n\r\nThe dragable bar is only 3 pixel in height, can this please be increased?\r\n\r\nSomething like 10px still looks nice. Maybe a symbol could also be added that this area can be resized?\r\n\r\nalso, please remove the empty space on the left and right of the console panel.\r\nThis just wastes spaces when one works on a smaller display (e.g. laptop).\r\n\r\nFor example, 10px height for the dragOpen div, no margin left and right, no round border.\r\n![image](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/assets/1223135/46464b61-e96b-4414-9bbf-0a8ddba37e84)\r\n\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
